Package: caretMultimodal
Title: Multimodal Late Fusion in R
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Josh", "Dyce", , "jpdyce@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    person("Amrit", "Singh", role = c("aut"))
Description: `caretMultimodal` extends the `caret` framework to support late fusion workflows in R,
    enabling users to train models independently across multiple data modalities and combine their
    predictions into a single meta-model. Designed for R developers, data scientists, and 
    biomedical researchers alike, `caretMultimodal` aims to make late fusion ensemble modelling
    as accessible and flexible as single-modality workflows in `caret`.
